{
  "stem": "9987.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were bringing in Russian-- I mean German prisoners, and I was doing translating from German to Russian for the kommandantur.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Finally, after about three months, artillery started firing-- Russian artillery-- firing for about 48 hours without a stop.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The whole-- they scorched the earth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And when they made a move, there was not a German in front in sight of them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the front started to move for approximately 100 kilometers, till it stopped around [INAUDIBLE] near the river [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I go back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We go back to the town that we are coming from, the-- the partisan group.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It didn't take long, and there was what do you call a [NON-ENGLISH] in-- in-- in-- in English?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They-- they went ahead-- the Russian army, the Soviet army, all young people that they were on the street, they grabbed them, took him into the kommandantur.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You're in the army now, including me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, I didn't think like anybody else, because my-- my-- I wanted to survive that war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In a bad way I wanted to survive that war after going all that through.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My mind kept still working, and since I was very acquainted with that commandant that was interviewing the German prisoners, and I was doing the translating, and he took over the kommandantur in that town, he was [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, he was a wounded officer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A wounded officer, that he was a commandant all the time in the--in the the back land.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I convinced him that he should keep me as his adjutant, and I'll be his translator for the German prisoners.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know the local population.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I know Russian.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I know Polish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I know German.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I can get you anything you want.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
